data.description: This is a place to call home! This property has a great central location between Douglasville, Newnan, Whitesburg, Villa Rica, and Carrollton. If a commute to Atlanta or the airport is necessary, you can easily avoid a large portion of the interstate from this location by taking one of the nearby highways you have access to from this location. The interior of this home has been extremely well maintained and has many high end finishes that you will love. From the beautiful hardwood floors, to the millwork on the ceilings and the granite countertops, there is beauty around every corner. This spacious home has an open floorplan with the master on the main level as well as two additional bedrooms on the main level. Upstairs there are two more bedrooms and the partially finished basement has yet another bedroom. Outside you will find a fenced in back yard with a fire pit, basketball goal and a lovely screened in porch. This home is located in a cul-de-sac. The roof is brand new and the septic tank has been pumped. All HVAC for the entire house is under 5 years old. Did we also mention the owner updated the shower in the master bathroom with a 15k shower?
